node.title: Body found in search for missing swimmer at Auckland Beach
node.description: The swimmer went missing on Friday evening.
node.content: ["Police have found a body in the search for a swimmer who went missing at Kariotahi Beach last week.", "The search at the south Auckland beach started after emergency services were notified on Friday night. The body was found by the Eagle helicopter on Tuesday morning as it was carrying out an aerial search of the coastline.", "Police said the body was recovered by local surf lifesavers and brought to land.", "\"Next of kin have been advised however police will not be in a position to name the person until formal identification has taken place,\" police said.", "The death will be referred to the Coroner."]
